description: All the guys - Kameron Scott, Justin Taylor, Ryan Star, Cameron Adams, Cody Springs, and Christian Cross - gather poolside to participate in their own sexual Olympics. It's one hungry jock on another as they compete to see who can suck the best, whose ass is the most fuckable and which he-man can shoot the farthest. They're all stars but Kameron takes the prize for his expert deep throating skills!
title: Road Trip, Vol. 7 - Napa Valley, Scene #03
